title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 3 Night' game

maintext:
BOISE, Idaho (AP) _ The winning numbers in Tuesday evening’s drawing of the Idaho Lottery’s “Pick 3 Night” game were:
7-7-4
(seven, seven, four)
